    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chicken breast strips</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4 min on each side until golden</p><p>Tip: Grind a generous amount of pepper onto the chicken for an extra kick of spice</p>",
